title: The Best Fits for Remaining Free Agents
description:
Nora, Steven, and Rodger discuss and pick their best fits for the remaining free agents and conclude the show by giving their spiciest takes heading into the season.

Host: Nora Princiotti, Steven Ruiz, and Rodger Sherman
Associate Producer: Stefan Anderson
Additional Production Supervision: Arjuna Ramgopal
